## Conclusion

No testable properties found in `pydantic.datetime_parse`.

**Analysis Summary:**
- `pydantic.datetime_parse` is a backport/migration module from Pydantic V1
- All datetime parsing functions (`parse_date`, `parse_datetime`, `parse_time`, `parse_duration`) were removed in Pydantic V2
- The module only contains `getattr_migration`, a PEP 562 implementation helper that raises import errors when accessing removed functions
- No actual datetime parsing logic exists in this module to test

The module serves only as a migration aid to provide helpful error messages for users upgrading from V1 to V2.
